[ti: Mirror, tell me honestly]
[ar: Jasper Nguyen]
[tool: LRC Maker https://lrc-maker.github.io]
[length: 03:58.320]
[00:00.302] [Intro]
[00:01.759] Mirror resting in my hands tonight
[00:05.425] Your reflection lives inside my mind
[00:08.860] One careless word escaped my lips
[00:12.055] Now silence cuts me every time
[00:18.089]
[00:29.380] [Verse 1]
[00:31.169] Mirror, don’t you fall asleep tonight
[00:33.858] This aching heart is buried way too deep inside
[00:37.309] The one she gave me right before she left
[00:40.465] Still holds her shadow in every breath
[00:43.846] I stare into the glass that she once held
[00:47.057] And see her smile like nothing ever fell
[00:50.541] I wish that I could reach through you somehow
[00:53.672] And bring her back before the light runs out
[00:55.594]
[00:56.225] [Pre-Chorus]
[00:57.074] Even through the darkest skies
[01:00.171] Even when the whole world cries
[01:03.176] Like waves that keep returning home
[01:06.654] I’m still reaching out for more
[01:09.361]
[01:09.909] [Chorus]
[01:10.915] Mirror, tell me honestly
[01:13.511] How much longer till she’s here with me?
[01:17.053] My heart keeps running to her light
[01:20.297] While my mind screams “Let’s leave tonight”
[01:24.032] I could drift above the clouds
[01:26.434] But I’m so scared of falling down
[01:29.669] This heart that burns so warm inside
[01:33.086] Still belongs to her, no place to hide
[01:39.662]
[01:40.921] [Verse 2]
[01:41.417] Mirror, I still wanna stay
[01:44.207] Though every thought just fades to gray
[01:46.925] Every little thing I see
[01:49.789] Always leads me back to her
[01:52.934] My heart still whispers out her name
[01:56.239] Though my mind plays the same old game
[01:59.496] No matter how I try to run
[02:02.946] She’s the only place my thoughts return
[02:05.066]
[02:06.037] [Pre-Chorus]
[02:06.294] Even through the pouring rain
[02:09.682] Even through the hurt and pain
[02:12.718] Like moonlight dancing on the sea
[02:16.370] She still has a hold on me
[02:19.024]
[02:19.432] [Chorus]
[02:20.720] Mirror, tell me honestly
[02:23.678] How much longer till she’s here with me?
[02:27.350] My heart keeps running to her light
[02:30.474] While my mind screams “Let’s leave tonight”
[02:33.856] I could drift above the clouds
[02:36.621] But I’m so scared of falling down
[02:39.946] This heart that burns so warm inside
[02:43.323] Still belongs to her, no place to hide
[02:46.237]
[02:47.626] [Bridge]
[02:48.440] Maybe love was never meant to be safe
[02:51.473] Maybe that’s the reason we still stay
[02:54.237] Somewhere between hope and endless fear
[02:57.946] I’m still wishing she was here
[03:01.549]
[03:01.775] [Final Chorus]
[03:05.068] Mirror, tell me honestly
[03:07.660] Will her heart ever beat for me?
[03:11.862] Though my mind keeps pulling free
[03:15.010] Love still lingers over me
[03:18.351] Every storm and every scar
[03:21.576] Only shows me who you are
[03:24.918] Mirror, tell me one last time
[03:28.710] Will her world one day meet mine?
[03:33.198]
[03:35.102] [Outro]
[03:35.625] Mirror trembling in my hand
[03:38.810] Love was never what I planned
[03:42.634] Still this restless heart of mine
[03:46.459] Would choose her every single time